foundly  changed  many  jobs,  it’s  not  just  manufacturers  that  rely  on  people  with
these skills.

Unfortunately,  today’s  students  do  not  seem  motivated  to  go  into  manufacturing
or pursue technician jobs. Many of them are unaware that manufacturing is a good
career path or that these jobs are even available. Their impressions, shaped by par-
