PREPARED STATEMENT OF REPRESENTATIVE EDDIE BERNICE JOHNSON

Thank you, Mr. Chairman.
Community  colleges  play  a  key  role  in  providing  access  to  tomorrow’s  high-tech-

nology workforce.

Of particular interest to me are minority-serving institutions such as Historically
Black Colleges and Universities and their importance in training students to fill to-
morrow’s high-tech jobs.

