didn’t  include  all  of  the  other  things  that  go  along  with  it,  it  was
just  labor,  material,  and  freight.  It  didn’t  include  all  of  the  other
stuff  about  how  the  customer  had  to  do  all  of  the  quality  things
and  educate  the  Chinese  workforce,  et  cetera,  et  cetera.  They  still
