ucts  are  not  taxed  just  because  they  are  made  here  in  the  United
States,  that  they  have  equal  competition,  not  just  here  in  the
United States, but overseas.

And  I  think  when  we  talk  about  jobs,  we  can’t  separate  it  from,
and—comments  from  the  panel.  I  apologize  for  ranting  on  and  on.
Ms.  POINDEXTER.  You  bring  up  a  very  good  point,  and  the  one
