Mr. BILBRAY. Thank you, Mr. Chairman.
Chairman  BAIRD.  Yes,  I  would  just  point  out  that  the  amount,
if I am not mistaken, for H1–B is about $1,500 per application, and
some  recent  studies  have  suggested  that  there  is  significant—in
